Summary: 4 lights moving same direction one minute apart and not moving straight
divs: sighting detailsat approx 8:50pm on 05\09\07 my friends and i were standing at the lake point and happened to notice what appeared to be a moving star. when i pointed it out we all noticed it was not a shooting star. then we thought it may be a satelite but it was not traveling like a satelite because the path it was going was straight at first but the it dropped and went back up and continued its path, then disappeared. shortly after, we saw another going the same direction, it also dropped and made a check mark like pattern, went back higher than original and then straight. about a minute after that we seen two more which did pretty much the same thing. could these be satelites?? has anyone ever seen anything like this before??
